                                                         \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/screenshot-2024-12-19-at-1-05-57-pm.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/screenshot-2024-12-19-at-1-05-57-pm.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/screenshot-2024-12-19-at-1-05-57-pm.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/screenshot-2024-12-19-at-1-05-57-pm.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"2872\" height=\"1492\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Ribblr home page with crochet and knit patterns\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/screenshot-2024-12-19-at-1-05-57-pm.png\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/screenshot-2024-12-19-at-1-05-57-pm.png\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eRibblr is similar to Ravelry in that it\u0026#39;s a database of user-created patterns for different yarn projects. You can use the search bar and filters to only look at free patterns in knitting, crochet, or both techniques. There\u0026#39;s an option to favorite patterns to return to later, and you can follow your favorite pattern creators on Ribblr to keep up with their latest projects. \u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eRibblr frequently hosts pattern giveaways, offers free patterns during holiday countdowns, and lets you start a virtual journal to track your progress in any given project. The home page also shows trending patterns, and when you click on a pattern, there will be an array of similar patterns to check out. \u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eThe one downside to Ribblr, however, is that you cannot access a printable PDF of a pattern because the platform is eco-friendly and trying to cut down on paper use. \u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"sarah-maker\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan\u003e5 \u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cspan\u003e\n                            \u003ca href=\"https://sarahmaker.com/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eSarah Maker\u003c/a\u003e\n                    \u003c/span\u003e\n       \u003c/h2\u003e\n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                            \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/sarah-maker-1.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/sarah-maker-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/sarah-maker-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/sarah-maker-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/sarah-maker-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/sarah-maker-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/sarah-maker-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/sarah-maker-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/sarah-maker-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"1758\" height=\"868\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"sarah maker homepage screenshot with crochet, cricut, punch needle, and sewing crafts\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/sarah-maker-1.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/sarah-maker-1.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe Sarah Maker crafts website, founded by a DIY enthusiast, is a great resource for finding arts and crafts ideas as well as learning new skills. Here, you can learn how to make your own quilts, clay jewelry, tie-dye clothing, festive ornaments, friendship bracelets, face masks, and embroider gorgeous patterns and badges.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eThere\u0026#39;s a designated section for crochet, where you can learn how to crochet scarves, hats, blankets, and more. The step-by-step crochet tutorials for beginners are great for those who are new to this hobby.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"all-free-crafts\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan\u003e6 \u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cspan\u003e\n                            \u003ca href=\"https://www.allfreecrafts.com\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eAll Free Crafts\u003c/a\u003e\n                    \u003c/span\u003e\n       \u003c/h2\u003e\n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                                                                        \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/screenshot-2024-12-19-at-1-07-04-pm.png\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/screenshot-2024-12-19-at-1-07-04-pm.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/screenshot-2024-12-19-at-1-07-04-pm.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/screenshot-2024-12-19-at-1-07-04-pm.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/screenshot-2024-12-19-at-1-07-04-pm.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/screenshot-2024-12-19-at-1-07-04-pm.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/screenshot-2024-12-19-at-1-07-04-pm.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/screenshot-2024-12-19-at-1-07-04-pm.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/screenshot-2024-12-19-at-1-07-04-pm.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"2462\" height=\"1320\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"All Free Crafts homepage with crafts for scone jars and construction paper reindeer\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/screenshot-2024-12-19-at-1-07-04-pm.png\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/screenshot-2024-12-19-at-1-07-04-pm.png\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eAll Free Crafts has all sorts of crafts for every skill level. You can sort the crafts by holiday and skill level, too, if you\u0026#39;re trying to create decorations for a holiday party. \u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eThere are entire sections dedicated to recycling common household items like old denim, cardboard, and even lightbulbs! This website also features lots of nature and outdoor crafts for hobbies like bird watching. For example, there are crafts to create your own bird feeders and birdhouses. \u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eThere are crafts for every kind of crafter on All Free Crafts. While there are sewing, knit, and crochet patterns, there are also others like a DIY scone jar, candles, paper crafts, and soaps. \u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"yarnspirations\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan\u003e7 \u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cspan\u003e\n                            \u003ca href=\"https://www.yarnspirations.com\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eYarnspirations\u003c/a\u003e\n                    \u003c/span\u003e\n       \u003c/h2\u003e\n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                                                                        \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/screenshot-2024-12-19-at-1-07-48-pm.png\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/screenshot-2024-12-19-at-1-07-48-pm.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/screenshot-2024-12-19-at-1-07-48-pm.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/screenshot-2024-12-19-at-1-07-48-pm.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/screenshot-2024-12-19-at-1-07-48-pm.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/screenshot-2024-12-19-at-1-07-48-pm.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/screenshot-2024-12-19-at-1-07-48-pm.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/screenshot-2024-12-19-at-1-07-48-pm.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/screenshot-2024-12-19-at-1-07-48-pm.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"2792\" height=\"1506\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Yarnspirations project page with options for crochet and knit clothing and stockings\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/screenshot-2024-12-19-at-1-07-48-pm.png\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/screenshot-2024-12-19-at-1-07-48-pm.png\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYarnspirations is a great website that offers free patterns for crochet and knit projects. You can sort the projects from beginner to advanced based on your skill level.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eThis website has all sorts of patterns, from blankets, to wearables like hats and skirts, to pillows and so much more. Yarnspirations partners with yarn brands like Red Heart and Caron, too, so you can purchase the yarn you need for a specific project directly from the website. It also provides yarn recommendations. \u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eThere are also a ton of free resources with beginner guides on how to knit and crochet, helpful tips, and even other crafting activities like macramé and quilting on the site. \u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eIt can be hard to come up with your own ideas for DIY projects, especially if you\u0026#39;re not a seasoned arts and crafts enthusiast. But with the sites we\u0026#39;ve listed here, you\u0026#39;ll have access to seemingly endless fun and creative DIY ideas, and for free too. Happy crafting!\u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
